About Event

​Start you year with Jane Milovanova

​📅 January 2, 2026 | ⏰ 3:00 PM
📍 Menlo Park, Silicon Valley (private house)

​🔹 Executive Concept

​Jane Milovanova, Founder & CEO of ISOUL Global Women’s Association, will be in Silicon Valley for one week only.

​You are invited to a private strategic session for women who want to design 2026 with precision, clarity, and long-term vision

​This is a high-level, calm, intellectually deep environment where we work with:

​vision,

​women leaders
